title: Should We Write Off Tom Brady?
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Bill Barnwell! On today’s show: Are you finally ready to write off Tom Brady? Is the Packers’ loss to the Commanders something they can bounce back from? Which surprising team among the Giants, Jets, and Seahawks should be a buyer at the trade deadline? Plus, we debate the struggling Lakers and 76ers and the thriving Jazz!
